Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he seem in a bad mood to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか機嫌悪そうじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go near him, we might get punched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,近寄ったら殴られかも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また来てる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.16,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hasegawa {\c&H27D9F9&}Ko{\c&HFFFFFF&}daka"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My same old life of being treated like a Yankee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらずヤンキー扱いされる毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The same old after-school hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらずの放課後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.25,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Common Room 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And our same old Neighbors Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:28.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そして相変わらずの我らが隣人部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おーす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.18,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kashiwazaki {\c&H27D9F9&}Se{\c&HFFFFFF&}na"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:42.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部屋間違えました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:46.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待ちなさいよ　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Kodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:47.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どう　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:50.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とても似合ってるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう って違うわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm asking you whether it's {\i1}funny!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,笑えるかって聞いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We were talking yesterday\Nabout how we could make friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:59.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日お笑いの技術を磨けば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,by polishing up our comedic skills, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,友達ができるって話になったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... So you did {\i1}this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:03.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに　それでこれか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　おもちゃ屋さんで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! The sign in the toy store said\N"Guaranteed to be a hit with everyone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,皆に馬鹿受け間違いなしって書いてあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの真に受けるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, don't take stuff like that seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't agree more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まったくだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, a high-level art such\Nas comedy was beyond Meat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:18.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり肉如きに笑いと言う高度な技術は無理だったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:19.82,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Mikazuki {\c&H27D9F9&}Yo{\c&HFFFFFF&}zora"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that getup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ なんだ　その格好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm cosplaying the most\Nlaughable creature in existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:25.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これはこの世で　もっとも滑稽な生物のコスプレだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kodaka? Funny, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ小鷹　面白いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばこれならどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Meat"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それって　もしかして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:41.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私　お金持ちで美少女みたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, like, so {\i1}rich{\i} and {\i1}pretty{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしはそんな喋り方じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私はそんな喋り方じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't {\i1}talk{\i} like {\i1}that!{\i} I'm, like,\Njust {\i1}rich{\i} and {\i1}pretty{\i} and that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:49.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お金持ちで美少女みたいな存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly makes me a laughable creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんであたしが滑稽な存在なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, that's not\Nfunny, it's just annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,って言うかそんなのむかつくだけで笑えないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But seeing you ranting and\Ncrying is always such a good time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:57.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　だが貴様が怒ったり泣いたりすると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私は愉快な気持ちになる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an awful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪ね　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Yozora, aren't you\Nembarrassed to be looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:04.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つーか　夜空　その格好恥ずかしくないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかお前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,True comedy is about more\Nthan just one-off gags like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:16.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真のお笑いっていうのはそんな一発ネタじゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to be\Ncondescending... you're just Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:18.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹のくせに上から目線じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see this "true comedy" you speak of, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ　ならば真のお笑いとやらを見せてもらおうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. True comedy... is about {\i1}talking{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　真のお笑い　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トークだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トーク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Talking"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I'll give you a\Ntaste of my hilarious talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞かせてやるぜ　俺の爆笑トーク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,タイトルは　「饅頭怖い」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The title is "Manju Buns Are Scary."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Man A says, " Right now\NI'm scared of some hot coffee!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すると　Ａさんはこう答えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「今は熱いコーヒーが怖い」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さむっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame.
