Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.95,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Haganai NEXT"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.11,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,想像しちゃダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:24.02,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more than I imagined... every{\i}\N{\i1}day's a roller coaster{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:24.10,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ジェットコースターな毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:31.19,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always barreled ahead with everything I had{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.01,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,引き締めて前を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.75,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも駆け抜けたら
