Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:06.98,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.47,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:14.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet I can even reach that star{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:14.08,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの星だって届きそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.82,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,418)}"My {\c&H8524E4&}Teen {\c&H14E4AC&}Years {\c&H0CE9FA&}SNA{\c&HFFFFFF&}FU"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お笑いですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, one does tend to think\Nof funny people as popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに面白い人は人気者ってイメージありますね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.35,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shiguma {\c&H27D9F9&}Ri{\c&HFFFFFF&}ka"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some tea, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴　お茶をどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have heard your funny story too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:31.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたくしも兄貴の面白い話を聞きたかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.69,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kusunoki {\c&H27D9F9&}Yuki{\c&HFFFFFF&}mura"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better off this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞かないほうがいいわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　あれはひどかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-At least I didn't try to get a few\Neasy laughs with my hairstyle like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,安易に髪型で笑いを取ろうとしたお前らよりマシだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of hairstyles, I recently\Ngot some very interesting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:46.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,髪型と言えば　この前興味深い情報を得たな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,According to a magazine I read,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,雑誌に書いてあったのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,something called a "pouf" is\Npopular around town right now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:53.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,都会のリア充共の間で「盛り」というものが流行っているらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,among people with actual lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「盛り」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pouf"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You literally poof up\Nyour hair to give it volume,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,文字通り髪を盛ってボリュームを増やし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you've got it really big,\Nyou put various decorations in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さらにその大きく盛った髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,様々なデコレーションを施すのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that might be kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　ちょっと面白そうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika's seen pictures on the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科もネットで写真見たことありますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They almost reminded me of\Nmedieval European nobility...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中世ヨーロッパの貴族見たいというかなんというか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobility? Hey, that's perfect for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴族　あたしにピッタリじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the really extreme ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,凄い者だと　髪の毛を鳥籠みたいに編んで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,people twist their hair into a\Nbirdcage and put in a real bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実際に小鳥を入れたり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or use big accessories\Nthat spell out the word "love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,愛の文字を象った大きな飾りをつけたりするんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be,\Na Warring States general?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ　戦国武将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they emphasize\Nindividuality over functionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:26.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,機能性よりも個性を重視している点では
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the overall concept may be the same as\Nthe one behind Warring States helmets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:29.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,戦国武将の兜とコンセプトは同じかもしれませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this "pouf," like the\Nhelmets of Warring States generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では「盛り」と言うのは戦国武将の兜のように
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is meant to serve as proof of\Nidentity for those beheaded in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:37.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,合戦で敵に首を取られた際に　己の身分を証明し
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so that their heads will receive\Nthe respect appropriate to their...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その首が身分相応に鄭重に扱われるようにとの目的を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:42.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,盛った髪型…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong, Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,違うぞ　幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残念です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't totally get it, but it\Ndoes seem kind of similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よくわかんないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかあれっぽいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite. It would take an\Nexceptional person to pull off the pouf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:50.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よほどの人物でなければ盛髪を御するのは難しい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose a commoner would\Nbe reckless to even attempt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,凡人が挑戦するのは無謀と言うものだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bore you with talk of\Nsomething so irrelevant to your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様とは無縁のつまらない話を振って悪かった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The safest bet for a commoner would be to\Nget an ordinary hairdo at an ordinary salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　一般人は普通に美容院に行き
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,普通に髪を整のえてもらうのが無難というものだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I do hope to see\Na pouf in real life one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:13.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　一度ぐらいはリアルで「盛り」を見てみたいものだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,True, it {\i1}would{\i} be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに難しいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There just aren't many people out there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,盛髪の強烈な自己主張さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:21.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,従属させるほどの高貴でゴージャスなオーラを発している
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with the naturally aristocratic\Nand gorgeous aura needed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to carry off the intense\Nself-assertiveness of the pouf style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生まれついての貴人なんてなかなかいませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,True... What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな　残念だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an obvious ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて態とらしい釣りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is one, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いるじゃない　ここに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,釣られた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An aristocrat overflowing with that very aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのオーラで捲くりの高貴なお方が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a woman alive\Nbetter suited to the pouf than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この世にあたしほど「盛り」が似合う偉人はいないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無理するな　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!\NThe pouf is an extremely tricky hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ　星奈先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「盛り」はとても難易度の高い髪型なんですから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a strain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無理じゃないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The aura of divinity I project from\Nwithin is enough to carry off {\i1}any{\i} hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな髪型だろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:51.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしの内面から湧き上がる神々しいオーラの前に従属させみてるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて簡単に引っかかるんだこいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such an easy mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If you're that set on it,\NI'll poof up your hair for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:58.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　そこまで言うなら今から貴様の髪を盛ってやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika has all sorts of tools in\Nher lab! Rika will go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科室に道具いろいろ揃ってますから取って来ますね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:03.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　用意はいいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything too crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり無茶なことしないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,動くな　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それではゆくぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty nice having\Nanother girl brush your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの女子に髪を梳いてもらうってなかなかいいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i0}'s hair is so\Nsmooth! And no split ends at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:27.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈先輩の髪って凄くさらさらですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,枝毛とかまったくないし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you credit for\Ngood hair, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の髪だけは褒めてやってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, your hair\Nis very pretty too. Rika's jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:36.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空先輩の髪もすっごい綺麗で羨ましいです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll give Yozora credit\Nfor good hair, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに　夜空も髪だけは褒めてあげていいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rika, yours is glossy and pretty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか　理科だって髪つやつやで綺麗じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こら　動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here, a refill.\N- Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お代わりは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.65,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's poofing time.\NAny requests, Meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ではいよいよ盛るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,肉　何か要望あるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me look like someone\Nwith a real life, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:56.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうね　それじゃリア充っぽい感じでお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A "has a life" theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テーマはリア充か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:01.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リア充といえば　夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Real social lives make me think... summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice! Then to give it a\N"girl with real life enjoying summer" feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ夏を満喫するリア充っぽい念じて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:10.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドは寄せて返す波打ち際をイメージしてウエーブに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wave the sides to evoke\Nthe image of rolling ocean waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it! Now let's try putting in\Nringlets to represent the swirling tides!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いい感じだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:16.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アクセントで渦潮イメージして縦ロールを混ぜてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:19.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらは夏の嵐をイメージして派手目のカールで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And this part will be a summer\Nstorm, so kind of flashy curls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうですか　星奈先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah, I think it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　いいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the top. Since the sides are the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ではトップだが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,横が海だから砂浜に盛られた城をイメージして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the top should be a sandcastle on the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about using a bikini instead of ribbons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リボンの代わりにビギニを使うのはどうです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, a watermelon and some\Nfireworks would complete that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後はスイカと花火が欲しいところだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bikini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ビギニ　スイカ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not {\i1}yakisoba{\i} while we're at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでに焼きそばだってどうです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前天才だな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yakisoba?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:42.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,焼きそば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go purchase a swimsuit,\Na watermelon, fireworks, and {\i1}yakisoba.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,水着とスイカと花火と焼きぞば　買ってまいります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:51.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまん　俺にはどうしようもない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Poke, poke, poke, poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly! Go on, fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飛べ　ほら飛べ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.79,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Takayama {\c&H27D9F9&}Ma{\c&HFFFFFF&}ria"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack! I'm doing it! I'm doing it,\Njust like I'm supposed to, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やってます　やってます　ちゃんとやってますのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　幸村か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Sister Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリア殿は何をなさっているのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The old hag is making me do forced\Nlabor as punishment for slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:18.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お仕事サボった罰で婆に強制労働させられているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.71,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I did something naughty. I'm very sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,っで　お前は何をしているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Sena-{\i1}anego{\i}\Nblah blah so on and so forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実は星奈の姉御がこれこれこういうわけで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you want something summery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夏っぽいのがほしいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　これを持っていくといいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,できた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it the " Ultimate-Satisfying-Social-Life-\NMeets-Midsummer-Night's-Dream Mega Max Pouf"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:44.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,名付けて「究極リア充＠真夏の夜の夢メガMAX盛り」だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:51.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おもっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You look super-cute, Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈先輩　超可愛いです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ひど過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に可愛いな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head would make a magnificent war trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,素晴らしい荷印です　星奈の姉御
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really? It looks that good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そう　そんなに似合う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it looks super-good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まじ　超似合いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not simply gaudy. It evokes the\Npoignantly ephemeral nature of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,単に派手だけではない　物の憐れを感じさせます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous. Now I wish I'd\Ntried a pouf before I cut my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,羨ましいな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私も髪を切る前に「盛り」をやっておけばよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this might be a real winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにこれ　結構いいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前ら正気か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What do you think, Kodaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どう　小鷹どう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It really expresses the group aesthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,凄くお前ららしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it just? Okay, I'm going home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　そろそろ帰るわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:41.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy was so mad at me when\NI got home yesterday! Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日家に帰ったら　パパにめちゃくちゃ怒られたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me lots spankings, and he\Nmade me put my hair back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:52.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お尻ぶたれたし　髪型も元に戻されたし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう最悪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Pegasus-{\i1}san.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ペガサスさん　グッジョブです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika got carried away by excitement yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日　テンション上がっちゃってましたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that she's calmed down,\Nshe realizes that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静に考えるとあれはなかったですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I went a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとやり過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let this end as a funny story! Dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せめて笑い話で終わらせてよ　馬鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the club meeting ended\Nin disappointment once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隣人部は今日も残念だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.21,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,ユー·ガット·メール
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.50,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an7\frz345\c&HE6E3DA&\3c&H7D685B&\pos(586,101)}Kashiwazaki Sena\NToday\N{\c&H7D685B&\3c&HE6E3DA&}\NWhy aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:39.17,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Studying for a test"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.19,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Unimportant! Come to the club room"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:49.02,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"It's important!\NIs something up in the club room?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.90,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Only Yukimura is here! (>__<)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.21,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\an7\c&HE6E3DA&\3c&H7D685B&\pos(429,189)}\h\h\h\h\h\hKashiwazaki Sena\N\h\h\h\h\h\hRe: Re: Re: Re: Re: Today\N{\c&H7D685B&\3c&HE6E3DA&}\N\N{\fscx85}Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i} just came (*^_^ *)\NDon't need you, Kodaka! (^^)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんちゃん　助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help me!\N- Kobato-{\i1}chan,{\i} wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん　待って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく　何やってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a scream come through the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,電話の向こうで悲鳴が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think someone was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:22.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか誘拐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,違うって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hasegawa {\c&H27D9F9&}Ko{\c&HFFFFFF&}bato"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.49,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,ユー·ガット·メール
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.91,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\an7\bord5\be5\pos(489,209)\frz2.235\c&HE6E3DA&\3c&H7D685B&}\h\h\h\h\hKashiwazaki Sena\N\h\h\h\h\hCome to think of it\N\N{\c&H7D685B&\3c&HE6E3DA&}{\fscx90}Kodaka, are you in\Nbad shape for finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.08,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Dunno"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.59,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Come to my house tomorrow, then.\NWe'll study together."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Sena's got the top GPA in our grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈の成績は学年一位らしいからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobato, I'm gonna study at\NSena's place for a while this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:09.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩　俺午後からちょっと星奈のとこで試験勉強してくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだったら　お前も来るか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:23.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くっくっく　くれぐれも気をつけるがいい　我が半身よ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My other half, I bid you take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり　行かないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ　怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で嫌われてんな　星奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She really hates you, Sena...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.05,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(113,546)}Private\NProperty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく来たな　小鷹君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来たわね　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, study hard for finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,では試験勉強を頑張りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy, are you done with Kodaka already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれパパ　小鷹とはもういいの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パパが事ある毎に　小鷹の様子はどうだって聞いてくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy's always asking me\Nhow you're doing, so I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he had something he\Nneeded to talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か大事な話でもあるのかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I-I am not constantly asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:20.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,べ　別にそんな頻繁に聞いとらんわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato asked me to look after\Nyou, so of course I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隼人から頼まれているからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にかけるのは当然のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よくわからない人だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Kodaka, let's study in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしの部屋で勉強しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:38.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　入って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こ　これは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うまく撮れてるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great pictures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk hardly ever lets her\Nguard down, so it was hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの馬鹿　なかなか隙を見せないから苦労をしたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ　お前が撮ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I got them on the\Nsly with my digital camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　デジカメでこっそり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,盗撮じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sneak photography!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! This girl is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こわっ　こいつこわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,な　何でまたそんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほらほら　見てこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is the same one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ　もしかしてこの前の
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! I bought it off Yozora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　夜空から買い取ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the phrase\N"perseverance for vengeance," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,臥薪嘗胆って言葉があるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't that from the ancient story\Nabout the guy who nursed his grudge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恨みを忘れないように毎日薪の上で寝たり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by sleeping on a pile of firewood\Nevery night and eating bitter liver meat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,苦手肝を舐めて生活を送り
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:34.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,復讐を果たしたっていう故事から生まれた言葉だな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,until he finally got revenge\Non his father's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりそういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By staring at Yozora's stupid\Nface every night at bedtime
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,毎晩寝る時に　夜空の馬鹿面を見ながら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,while inhaling the scent of the wig she wore,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空のかぶったかつらのにおいを嗅ぐことで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the humiliation she's put me through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつに味合わされた屈辱を思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and psych myself up about\Nsomeday making her pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつかあの馬鹿をとっちめてやるって気持ちを奮い立たせてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One day I'm gonna make\Nthat jerk beg me for mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつかあの馬鹿を「ギャフン」と言わせてやるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwazaki Sena... A fearsome\Nwoman in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柏崎星奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんな意味で恐ろしい女だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, it's about this problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いいえ　この問題だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I already solved that one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは解いて上げたでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, my issue is that\NI don't know {\i1}how to{\i} solve it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう　答えだけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,解き方がわかんなくて困ってるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not just that I need the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why can't you get\Nsomething so easy? Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ　何でこんなのもわからないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿じゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll do the rest myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった　もう自分でやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさとしなさいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how can someone be\Nso {\i1}not{\i} geared for teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく　こいつ人に教えるのに向いてなさすぎだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought you some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お飲み物をお持ち致しました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Kodaka-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お久しぶりです　小鷹様
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How are matters progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,進展の方はいかがですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not too badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　ぼちぼちです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Please use this, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,然様ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,宜しければお使いください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それではごゆっくり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka, what did Stella give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:56.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹　ステラから何もらったの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella-{\i1}san{\i} is way too mysterious for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ステラさん　謎の人過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見せなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やめ　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見せなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何見てるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't looking at anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別に　何も見てねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm sick of studying. Want to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強飽きちゃったからゲームでもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A game? Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームって お前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's okay as\Nlong as it's just a little breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:25.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　気分転換にちょっとやるぐらいならいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do this one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オーケー　じゃあこれね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've played that one with Kobato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それなら小鳩とやったことあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you own it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も持ってたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just recently bought it.\NKobato-{\i1}chan{\i} loves the anime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最近買ったばかりなの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん　これのアニメが大好きなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all the Blu-rays a while back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間　ブルーレイ全巻揃えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't watched them yet, but\Nnext time Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i} comes over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ見てないけど　今度小鳩ちゃんがうちに来た時に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I didn't bring Kobato with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩連れてこなくてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter the very soul of my\Nenemy! Nine Lives Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:58.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,魂ごと打ち砕け　ナインダイブスブレイカー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmph! Amateur.\N- That makes a ten-win streak for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これであたしの十連勝ね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, and you were a total\Nn00b in the beginning, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,始めは完全に初心者だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius at everything, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしって　何をやっても天才なのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しいが否定できねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could deny that, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's evening already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,っで　もう夕方じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.53,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\an7\frz343\pos(350,112)\fscx80\c&H3C67B4&\3c&HC2D7E9&\b1}The Essence of Math
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't get any\Nstudying for finals done at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:30.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,結局全然試験勉強にならなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺そろそろ帰るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼します　お嬢様　小鷹様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena-{\i1}sama{\i0}, Kodaka-{\i1}sama{\i0}, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,御食事の準備が出来ました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her. Have some\Nfood before you go, Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって　食べて行きなさいよ　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ご馳走様でした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　俺はそろそろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better be getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:55.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜は泊まっていきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,泊まっていきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.67,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\an7\pos(341,240)\frz13.14\c&HE6E3DA&\3c&H78675D&\b1}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hKobato\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCan't come home tonight\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H78675D&\3c&HF4F3EF&\fscx90}Eat some cup noodles or whatever's\Nin the fridge for supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:23.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああー　何時かの空の下へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Ah, beneath that long-ago sky! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I always seem to get thrown off\Nbalance when I visit this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかこの家来ると調子狂うんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,President?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,背中を流そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you, but that's quite all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,結構です　遠慮します
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as circumspect as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらず君は慎み深いな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato would be tossing\Nthe soap at me without a care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隼人ならば何も気にせず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,石鹸も投げて起こしてくるところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし気にすることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no need for such concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It really concerns me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にするっつうの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think that's good, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　いいと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of the first time\NHayato ever took me to a bathhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:05.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしていると隼人に初めて銭湯に連れて行かれた時のことを思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,時に小鷹君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my daughter being bullied\Nat school, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの星奈はもしかして学校でいじめられているのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことはないと思いますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:24.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実は先日　星奈が頭にイカ焼きやら焼きそばを載せて帰ってきたことがあってな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena came home with fried\Nsquid and {\i1}yakisoba{\i} on her head...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be hard to believe, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,信じられないかもしれないが　本当のことなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そんなことが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time she told me "This is a\Nhigh-class hairstyle worthy of my greatness,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:34.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈は「これは自分に相応しい最高のヘアスタイルだ」などごまかすので
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:38.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時は厳しく叱ってしまったのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I scolded her harshly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that I've calmed down,\NI can't imagine such a foolish style exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:43.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静に考えてあんな戯けた髪型があるとは思えん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a very proud young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれはプライドの高い娘だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I worried that she might\Nhave said those absurd things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:49.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いじめを受けたのもごまかすため強がりであんな戯言を言ったかもしれんと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to hide the fact that she'd been bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心配になってな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう　理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been inside Sena's bedroom recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最近星奈の部屋に入られた事は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, ever since she entered high school
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　高校生になったあたりから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,she hasn't liked me to go into her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私が部屋に入るのを嫌がるようになってな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for a girl that age, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　あの年頃の娘なら仕方あるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, your daughter's\Nactually turned into a creepy stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長　実は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:14.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの娘さん　変態ストーカー化してますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて言えねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think she's\Nbeing bullied, Sir. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　いじめを受けてることはないと思いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,多分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だといいが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,も　もしも星奈がいじめられてるような事があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear that if Sena were ever\Nto get bullied, I would protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が絶対に守りますから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから安心してください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You would? Yes, you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she's in your care, Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NI know she'll be in good hands with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ　小鷹君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君ならば星奈が任せられる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:43.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,って　任せる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"In your care"? That seems kind of overblown...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だか大げさだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, I had yet to realize\Nthat I was getting steadily mired
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がどんどん取り返しのつかない状況になっていることに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in a situation beyond all salvaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:57.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この時の俺はまだ気付いていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, Yozora! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:02.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空　いつか見てなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A stray cloud blocks my view{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:34.47,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,光ったはずの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:39.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the star I know should be shining there{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.65,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,迷った雲が邪魔して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.67,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:43.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I believe in?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:43.14,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を信じたらいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.12,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was on my way to breaking{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.40,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:52.96,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The treasure bred in this all too changeable world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:52.43,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,育った宝物壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:57.06,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I was afraid of losing it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:56.17,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なくすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.36,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those days of sighing "This is absurd"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:58.94,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:00.13,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:03.68,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかどうで足掻いてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:03.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And flailing inside my birdcage{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:09.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were gazing up at the same sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:07.93,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:09.79,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:16.11,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I gripped your hand,{\i}\N{\i1}you gripped back, didn't you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.16,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の手を握った時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:16.42,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:22.65,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These joined hands are stronger than any wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:19.51,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繋がったこの手は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:22.82,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:29.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can fly higher even without wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.02,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,翼だってなくったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:29.32,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:32.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I know we'll be okay trying now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:32.75,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと今なら大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:38.33,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's grab the stars twinkling in the sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.01,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよ　テレビアニメ第二季が始まったな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The anime's second season has begun at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:46.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二季では髪を切ってついに本気を出した私が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.91,0:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In Season 2, now that I've cut my hair\Nand I'm not playing around anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:48.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,メインヒロインに相応しい大活躍をして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly I'll do remarkable\Nthings worthy of the main heroine,
